        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "When I'm trying to use this backend i get two errors. First is triggered by mkdir function in Zend\/Cache\/Backend\/Static.php on line 244. The directory id prepended by \/ and looks like this:\r\n\/C:\\wamp\\www\\projectname\\...\r\nSecond error is triggered by file_put_contents function in Zend\/Cache\/Backend\/Static.php on line 209 because file name is invalid - C:\\wamp\\www\\projectname\\html.\/\\x120html. "
        },
